title: FRIDAY - Super Wildcard Weekend is here!  2021
itunes:title: FRIDAY - Super Wildcard Weekend is here!  2021
description:
The postseason gets underway this weekend, and we'll have the latest injury updates including Stefon Diggs (0:34) and Jared Goff (1:36). The Browns dealing with COVID-19 issues as they'll be without head coach Kevin Stefanski and some key players, but Baker Mayfield is up for the challenge (:49). Deshaun Watson (3:06) not happy in Houston, plus we'll have the latest on head coaching interviews from around the league (3:34)
